OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FAn attack on four Jewish community
OL,7,Fambulances in North London is "so
OL,8,Fwarped it defies words", the home
OL,9,Fsecretary said on Monday night.
OL,11,FShabana Mahmood said the arson attack
OL,12,Fwas an attack "on this country and on
OL,13,Fus all", saying it will have caused
OL,14,F"distress and anxiety" for the Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,17,FShe was speaking at the annual dinner
OL,18,Fof Community Security Trust, the
OL,19,Fcharity that monitors antisemitism in
OL,20,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
