OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism police are leading
OL,7,Fthe investigation into the attack on
OL,8,Ffour ambulances belonging to a Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity charity in Golders Green,
OL,10,FNorth London.
OL,12,FThe incident is being treated as an
OL,13,Fantisemitic hate crime by the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police and has not been
OL,15,Fdeclared a terrorist incident, the
OL,16,Fforce said.
OL,18,FPolice have since set up an online
OL,19,Fportal for members of the public to
OL,20,Fshare any video footage they have
OL,21,Fbefore, during or after the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
