OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FThere were no injuries reported in the
OL,7,Fattack on the Jewish community
OL,8,Fambulance service, Hatzola, in
OL,9,FHighfield Road, at around 1.45am, and
OL,10,Fno arrests have yet been made.
OL,12,FMultiple cylinders on the vehicles had
OL,13,Fexploded during the fire, causing
OL,14,Fwindows to break in an adjacent block
OL,15,Fof flats.
OL,17,FHatzola is a non-profit, volunteer
OL,18,Forganisation that provides hospital
OL,19,Ftransportation and emergency care to
OL,20,Fthe local community, regardless of
OL,21,Freligion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
