SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FPolice will be engaging with faith
OL,7,Fleaders and carrying out additional
OL,8,Fpatrols in the area while the
OL,9,Finvestigation continues,
OL,10,FSuperintendent Sarah Jackson said.
OL,12,FChief Rabbi Ephraim Mirvis tells ITV
OL,13,FNews that the attack was by those "who
OL,14,Fseek to destroy life"
OL,16,FDuring her speech, the home secretary
OL,17,Fpledged that those behind the attack
OL,18,Fwill be pursued and made to face the
OL,19,Fconsequences of their "vile actions".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
