SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,F"Today, Jews in this country are being
OL,7,Fforced to live a smaller life: they
OL,8,Fare hiding the signs of their faith.
OL,9,FThey are fearful as they send their
OL,10,Fchildren to school, even when they
OL,11,Fattend a hospital appointment," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"And, of course, they attend
OL,15,Fsynagogues that require physical
OL,16,Fsecurity, as we here know all too well.
OL,18,F"History has repeatedly screamed its
OL,19,Fwarning at us. And yet, here we are
OL,20,Fagain, in 2026, with the oldest hatred
OL,21,Frising once more."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
