OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FChief Rabbi Ephraim Mirvis described
OL,7,Fthe attack as "particularly sickening".
OL,9,FHe told ITV News: "To attack
OL,10,Fambulances which exist for the sake of
OL,11,Fhelping people to be well and
OL,12,Fpreserving life.
OL,14,F"Here we are seeing displayed before
OL,15,Four eyes the forces of those who seek
OL,16,Fto destroy life as opposed to those
OL,17,Fwho are here to protect life."
OL,19,FCCTV shows three people in hoods
OL,20,Fpouring accelerant on the vehicles.
OL,21,FCredit: Jewish Community Council
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@fO]
