OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FSpeaking near the scene on Monday,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,8,FWilliams, who leads policing for the
OL,9,Farea, said investigators are aware of
OL,10,Fa group apparently claiming
OL,11,Fresponsibility for the attack online,
OL,12,Fbut have not yet verified whether this
OL,13,Fis true.
OL,15,FA video has allegedly been posted on
OL,16,FTelegram by an Islamist group called
OL,17,FHarakat Ashab al-Yamin al-Islamia,
OL,18,Fshowing a map of the location where
OL,19,Fthe ambulances were kept and footage
OL,20,Fof them on fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
