OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FCCTV shows three people in hoods
OL,7,Fpouring accelerant on the vehicles,
OL,8,Fwhich belong to the Jewish community
OL,9,Fambulance service, Hatzola, before
OL,10,Fsetting them on fire and running away.
OL,12,FThe service is a short walk from the
OL,13,FNorth Western Reform Synagogue
OL,14,F(Alyth), which marked its 90th
OL,15,Fanniversary in 2023.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
