OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fconfirmed the London Ambulance Service
OL,8,Fwill provide additional support in
OL,9,FGolders Green, and that the government
OL,10,Fwill fund replacement ambulances after
OL,11,Fthe "appalling" attack.
OL,13,F"This is a horrific antisemitic
OL,14,Fattack, and of course, my thoughts, I
OL,15,Fthink all our thoughts, will be with
OL,16,Fthose in the vicinity; the residents
OL,17,Fwho are understandably very concerned,
OL,18,Fthe Jewish community across the
OL,19,Fcountry, deeply concerned," Prime
OL,20,FMinister Keir Starmer said on Monday.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
