PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FThe PM said he had already been in
OL,7,Ftouch with community leaders on Monday
OL,8,Fmorning and would continue to be for
OL,9,Fthe rest of the day.
OL,11,F"Antisemitism has no place in our
OL,12,Fsociety and it's really important that
OL,13,Fwe all stand together in a moment like
OL,14,Fthis," Starmer said.
OL,16,FShomrim, a non-profit organisation
OL,17,Fwhich operates a neighbourhood watch
OL,18,Fin the area, condemned the attack on
OL,19,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
