PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,F"This was not only a criminal act of
OL,7,Farson, but a targeted and deeply
OL,8,Fconcerning incident affecting a vital
OL,9,Femergency service serving the local
OL,10,FJewish community," it said in a post
OL,11,Fon X.
OL,13,FShomrim said the north-west London
OL,14,Ffacility run by fellow Jewish charity
OL,15,FHatzola remained fully operational.
OL,17,FDamon Hoff, president of Machzike
OL,18,FHadath Synagogue, where the ambulances
OL,19,Fwere parked, said the community was
OL,20,Ffeeling vulnerable.
OL,26,@rD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
