OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FHe said: "When you attack a place of
OL,7,Fworship, and you attack ambulances,
OL,8,Fyou're going for the very heart and
OL,9,Fcore of what's decent about this
OL,10,Fcountry, and there must be outrage for
OL,11,Fthat.
OL,13,F"The political establishment needs to
OL,14,Fknow that there are many decent
OL,15,FBritons that are going to feel
OL,16,Fvulnerable. In a time like this, this
OL,17,Fis, you need the very best of humanity.
OL,19,F"The community is feeling vulnerable
OL,20,Fand feeling frightened, but we're not
OL,21,Fgoing to let that get us down."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
