OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FResponding to the attack, Conservative
OL,7,Fleader Kemi Badenoch said: "What kind
OL,8,Fof person targets Hatzola, a volunteer-
OL,9,Frun ambulance service?
OL,11,F"Just last week in Golders Green,
OL,12,Fmembers of the Jewish community told
OL,13,Fme how they live in fear of constant
OL,14,Fattacks.
OL,16,F"The police must find those
OL,17,Fresponsible. A hatred of Jews is
OL,18,Fgrowing in our country, and all of us
OL,19,Fneed to make it clear in our words and
OL,20,Factions that Britain will not tolerate
OL,21,Fantisemitism."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
