OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FLondon Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan said it
OL,7,Fwas a "cowardly attack on the Jewish
OL,8,Fcommunity" and insisted "Londoners
OL,9,Fwill never be cowed by this kind of
OL,10,Fhatred and intimidation".
OL,12,FSpeaking to people at the site of the
OL,13,Fattack, Reform's candidate for mayor
OL,14,Fof London, Laila Cunningham, said:
OL,15,F"Every Jewish person should be
OL,16,Fterrified, but so should every
OL,17,FLondoner.
OL,26,@oD@GOUpD@JO]pD@YOUrD@XO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
