OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774422265
OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,F"If we don't protect every single
OL,7,Fcommunity and we allow the
OL,8,Fglorification of any kind of
OL,9,Fintimidation of any group, in
OL,10,Fparticular, now the Jewish group, then
OL,11,Four streets belong to extremists, and
OL,12,Fno longer belong to us."
OL,14,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury condemned
OL,15,Fthe "appalling antisemitic attack",
OL,16,Fwhile the British Medical Association
OL,17,F(BMA) criticised "deliberate attacks
OL,18,Fon healthcare services" as
OL,19,F"reprehensible".
