OL,3,CArson attack on Jewish ambulances is
OL,4,C'attack on us all', Home Secretary says
OL,6,FThe number of antisemitic incidents
OL,7,Freported across the UK has risen since
OL,8,Flate 2023, according to the Community
OL,9,FSecurity Trust, which works to protect
OL,10,Fthe Jewish community, with 3,700
OL,11,Frecorded in 2025, up from 1,662 in
OL,12,F2022.
OL,14,FAnyone with any video or audio footage
OL,15,Fthat may be useful to the
OL,16,Finvestigation is asked to send it to
OL,17,Fwww.ukpoliceimageappeal.co.uk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
